{
  "texts": [
    "We present the first comprehensive survey of recent advancements in applying LLMs to psychotherapy.",
    "We introduce a conceptual taxonomy that organizes psychotherapy into three core components-Assessment, Diagnosis, and Treatment-and details their dynamic interrelations (Section §2).",
    "We review how LLMs are applied within these components, highlighting their roles in facilitating assessments, refining diagnostic processes, and enhancing treatment strategies (Section §3).",
    "We examine current research trends, including symptom and language coverage as well as the distribution of various models and techniques (Section §4).",
    "Finally, we discuss open challenges and outline promising directions for future work (Section §5)."
  ]
}